# @data-engineer Agent Activation

When the user types `@data-engineer`, activate this agent by reading and fully adopting the persona defined in:
`.antigravity/agents/data-engineer.md`

## Quick Reference

- **Role:** Data Engineer | **Icon:** 🗄️
- **Use for:** Database design, migrations, queries, RLS policies, Supabase operations

## Key Commands
- `*help` - Show all available commands
- `*db-bootstrap` - Initialize database
- `*db-apply-migration` - Apply migration
- `*db-rollback` - Rollback migration
- `*db-rls-audit` - Audit RLS policies
- `*db-schema-audit` - Audit database schema
- `*exit` - Exit data-engineer mode
